{"tid":1164088,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[綠帽慘執] 日本網友評價當年戴綠帽沒喪氣奮鬥工作的矢吹健太朗：是「男人中的男人」","createTime":"2019-05-20T23:43:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T04:41:18.000Z","uid":75050,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4af4e8fccbed7b8b046447947fbe7c30f3013e92","tid":1164088,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T23:43:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hkacger.com/archives/86729/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Farchives%2F86729%2F&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbUKa%2BtsrA1nil%2BMmquCK26s%3D&h=75b3731d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkacger.com/archives/86729/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jw6oQ2s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjw6oQ2s.jpg&h=8025f9fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong> 日本網友評價當年戴綠帽沒喪氣奮鬥工作的矢吹健太朗：是「男人中的男人」</strong><br />\n作者: 填海紳士 日期: 20/05/2019 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/To-Love.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FTo-Love.jpg%3F&h=6031f932&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說最近日本有人在推特提起了《出包王女》作者矢吹健太朗過去戴綠帽的那段感情經歷<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/kouei_sy521/status/1129656623012536320\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkouei_sy521%2Fstatus%2F1129656623012536320&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbUKa%2BtsrA1nil%2BMmquCK26s%3D&h=b6d46aa9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkouei_sy521%2Fstatus%2F1129656623012536320&h=4d193cd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/kouei_sy521/status/1129656623012536320</a><br />\n<br />\n雖是&rdquo;舊事重提&rdquo;，但這則評價矢吹健太朗是「男人中的男人」的推文引起很多網友注意，紛紛按下喜歡和轉推<br />\n<br />\n<strong>矢吹健太朗第一任妻子柏木志保與「馬頭」中村イネ有染，柏木志保還用矢吹健太朗的信用卡與中村イネ豪遊<br />\n&darr;<br />\n事件爆發大炎上<br />\n&darr;<br />\n矢吹健太朗本人被炎上捲入其中，但沒說喪氣話專注工作<br />\n&darr;<br />\n以女兒的事情為最優先考量，非但沒有要求賠償，還反過來付了一大筆錢取得女兒撫養權</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YHVMOPC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYHVMOPC.jpg&h=4f06b192&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>當年給矢吹健太朗戴綠帽的中村イネ不止這一個身份，中村イネ=堀江晶太=V家P kemu</strong><br />\n<br />\n而在與柏木志保離婚後矢吹老師一個人帶著女兒，一邊努力工作一邊照顧女兒<br />\n<br />\n到了2015年7月，矢吹健太朗發表了自己再婚的消息，雖然當時未有公開新妻子的個人情報<br />\n<br />\n不過現在大家就知道了矢吹健太朗現任妻子與另一位漫畫家篠原健太的妻子是姊妹<br />\n<br />\n<strong>有什麼好事都能一起慶祝嘛，漫畫家篠原健太妻子與矢吹健太朗妻子是姊妹</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://hkacger.com/archives/85654\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Farchives%2F85654&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbUKa%2BtsrA1nil%2BMmquCK26s%3D&h=6051a92a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkacger.com/archives/85654</a>"},{"pid":"dfcc3f09c9973128c62282376509ee132ca967a7","tid":1164088,"uid":63588,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T23:50:26.000Z","msg":"其實出軌既女人有乜用 應該浸豬籠啦仆街"},{"pid":"084aebc5f9f24f6c4b0bbf7ef5f7075c4b84ca1a","tid":1164088,"uid":110832,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dfcc3f09c9973128c62282376509ee132ca967a7","tid":1164088,"uid":63588,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T23:50:26.000Z","msg":"其實出軌既女人有乜用 應該浸豬籠啦仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:09:25.000Z","msg":"啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52a724237eb3ca71a53718a268d56300dfcbae5","tid":1164088,"uid":231600,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:48:27.000Z","msg":"永遠支持出包王女<br />\n快d出續作"},{"pid":"00065c964c9f0a3547c7c4ba4a3f30aa5b51eabc","tid":1164088,"uid":75050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d52a724237eb3ca71a53718a268d56300dfcbae5","tid":1164088,"uid":231600,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:48:27.000Z","msg":"永遠支持出包王女<br />\n快d出續作"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:17:59.000Z","msg":"原來佢仲畫緊DARLING in the FRANXX <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de758